ProxiQuest is an interactive Raspberry Pi-powered game that challenges players to combine quick thinking, precise button presses, and physical movement. Using LEDs, push buttons, and an ultrasonic distance sensor, players must respond to randomized prompts by pressing the correct button while positioning themselves within a specific distance range.
 Objective
Score as many points as possible by:
- Pressing the correct button when prompted
- Standing within the target distance range (e.g., 10â€“30 cm)
